    "For instance, we have demonstrated the random audio sample from the dataset before removing the noise from it in Fig. 5.",
    "Furthermore, Fig. 6 shows the audio sample waveform after the removal of noise from it and results in a much clearer waveform.",
    "Finally, the third step includes the trimming of the audio sample after the removal of noise as shown in Fig. 7.",
    "For the rest of the audio samples of different classes, we have illustrated the final trimmed waveform which is used for the feature extraction process followed by the classification process in Fig. 4.",
    "The samples shown for illustrations are included in the classification."
